It was really easy and safe. I bought the illusion potions in the bazaar for around 150pp each. <br>
Just cast the illusion on yourself when you zone into KOS areas-the (good) towns. I'm not really for sure how long they last, but never had one wear off. Of course when you zone out the illusion is gone. It's not real cheap,<br>
but they worked like a charm, and didn't have any problems )<br>
